h$, $
h = 6\gh-3$, $2\sum_{k=1}^{
h} \zh_k = -\len_\gamma$). Let $\zt_1,\zh_1$ be eliminated by these constraints. Define a complex "twist" variable $ eta_\gamma$ (conjugate to $\len_\gamma$), and consider the coordinate set $\{\zt_i\}_{i=2}^{
